@tvanfosson:
&gt; shouldn’t you be including the author attribution information as well?

No, because we are not republishing content. The twitter feeds are simply creating notices with links to content. It's no more about republishing content than if I wrote, "Hey! Go read this great book about <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Here-Comes-Everybody-Organizing-Organizations/dp/0143114948/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1294852217&amp;sr=8-1" rel="nofollow">online cultures</a>."
